%%{init: {'theme': 'base', 'themeVariables': {'actorBkg': '#FFF3E0', 'actorBorder': '#EF6C00', 'signalColor': '#333333', 'fontSize': '13px'}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Confidential Client
    participant TE as Token Endpoint
    participant CAM as Client Auth<br/>Middleware
    participant GH as Client Credentials<br/>Grant Handler
    participant TS as Token Service

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        C->>TE: POST /oauth2/token<br/>grant_type=client_credentials<br/>scope=...<br/>Authorization: Basic base64(id:secret)
    end

    rect rgb(243, 229, 245)
        TE->>CAM: Client Auth Middleware
        Note over CAM: Validate credentials<br/>(SHA-256 constant-time compare)
        CAM-->>TE: Client authenticated

        Note over TE: Validate client_credentials<br/>grant allowed for app
        TE->>GH: ValidateGrant + HandleGrant
        Note over GH: Determine audience:<br/>resource param or client_id
        GH->>TS: BuildAccessToken<br/>(sub = client_id, no user claims)
        TS-->>GH: Access token (JWT)
        GH-->>TE: Token response

        Note over TE: No refresh token, no id_token<br/>for client_credentials grant
        TE-->>C: 200 OK<br/>{ access_token, token_type,<br/>  expires_in }<br/>Cache-Control: no-store
    end
